    <item>
      <title>与美联储相比，日本央行 2024 年加息将再次表现异常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/boj-set-to-be-outlier-again-as-2024-hike-seen-in-contrast-to-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在长达数十年的战胜通货紧缩的努力中，日本央行已经习惯于成为政策上的局外人。 2024 年情况可能不会有什么不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/boj-set-to-be-outlier-again-as-2024-hike-seen-in-contrast-to-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 03:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注美联储转向，美元跌至八月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周四跌至四个月低点，因为交易员消化了迄今为止最明确的信号，即美联储激进的加息行动已经结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 01:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
